---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" lang="en">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-background">
    <header class="sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-border bg-background/80 backdrop-blur-md">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="flex items-center h-16">
          <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3 hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity">
            <img src="/favicon.png" alt="" class="w-8 h-8" aria-hidden="true" />
            <span class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight">Choorai</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8">
        <p class="text-text-secondary">Last updated: January 31, 2025</p>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Article 1 (Collection of Personal Information)</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            Choorai (hereinafter "the Service") collects minimal personal information from users. Currently, the Service does not have a sign-up feature, and only the following anonymous information may be automatically collected:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Pages visited and time spent (for web analytics)</li>
            <li>Browser type and operating system</li>
            <li>Country/region of access (based on IP address, anonymized)</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Article 2 (Purpose of Collection)</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            The collected anonymous information is used only for the following purposes:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Service usage statistics analysis</li>
            <li>Content improvement and user experience enhancement</li>
            <li>Technical issue resolution</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Article 3 (Retention and Disposal of Personal Information)</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            The collected anonymous analytics data is retained for service improvement purposes. No personally identifiable information is collected. If a membership feature is added in the future, this policy will be updated accordingly.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Article 4 (Sharing Personal Information with Third Parties)</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            The Service does not share users' personal information with third parties. However, exceptions are made in the following cases:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>When required by law</li>
            <li>When requested for investigation purposes through legally prescribed procedures</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Article 5 (Use of Cookies)</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            The Service may use cookies to enhance the user experience. Cookies are used for the following purposes:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Saving learning progress (local storage)</li>
            <li>Maintaining user preferences</li>
            <li>Web analytics (anonymized visit statistics)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            You can refuse the use of cookies through your browser settings, but some features may be limited.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Article 6 (User Rights)</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            Users may exercise the following rights:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Delete browser local storage and cookies</li>
            <li>Opt out of web analytics tracking (Do Not Track setting)</li>
            <li>Inquire about or raise objections to the processing of personal information</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Article 7 (Security Measures for Personal Information)</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            The Service maintains information security through the following measures:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Encrypted communication via HTTPS</li>
            <li>Collection of only minimal data</li>
            <li>Regular security reviews</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Article 8 (Changes to This Policy)</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            If this Privacy Policy is changed, the changes will be announced on the website. Significant changes will be announced at least 7 days in advance.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Article 9 (Contact)</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            For inquiries about personal information processing, please submit them through <a href="https://github.com/curogom/choorai/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">GitHub Issues</a>.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-border">
        <a href="/" class="text-primary hover:underline flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18" />
          </svg>
          Back to Home
        </a>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
